        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-purple-700 mb-2">Computer Science</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Foundations and advanced topics in computing.</p>
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=computer+science+engineering+lectures" target="_blank" class="bg-purple-700 hover:bg-purple-800 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded transition">Watch on YouTube</a>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 flex flex-col items-start hover:shadow-xl transition">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-purple-700 mb-2">Data Science</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Data analysis, machine learning, and big data.</p>
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=data+science+engineering+lectures" target="_blank" class="bg-purple-700 hover:bg-purple-800 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded transition">Watch on YouTube</a>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 flex flex-col items-start hover:shadow-xl transition">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-purple-700 mb-2">Artificial Intelligence</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">AI concepts, deep learning, and applications.</p>
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=artificial+intelligence+engineering+lectures" target="_blank" class="bg-purple-700 hover:bg-purple-800 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded transition">Watch on YouTube</a>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6 flex flex-col items-start hover:shadow-xl transition">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-purple-700 mb-2">Computer Engineering</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Hardware, software, and systems integration.</p>
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=computer+engineering+lectures" target="_blank" class="bg-purple-700 hover:bg-purple-800 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded transition">Watch on YouTube</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
